# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Dependencies
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
/node_modules
/.pnp
.pnp.*
.yarn/*
!.yarn/patches
!.yarn/plugins
!.yarn/releases
!.yarn/versions

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Testing
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
/coverage

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Next.js
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
/.next/
/out/

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Production builds
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
/build
/dist

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Miscellaneous
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.pem

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Debug logs
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment files
# (Falls du bestimmte .env-Dateien versionieren möchtest,
# diese Regeln entsprechend anpassen.)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.env*

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Deployment
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.vercel

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# TypeScript artifacts
# (Auch wenn du kein TypeScript nutzt, kann Next.js diese Dateien erzeugen.)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.tsbuildinfo
next-env.d.ts

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# JetBrains IDE (WebStorm, IntelliJ, etc.)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------

# Einfachste Variante: gesamten .idea-Ordner ignorieren
.idea/

# Falls du später Team-Einstellungen teilen möchtest,
# kannst du stattdessen .idea/ entfernen und nur
# benutzerspezifische Dateien ignorieren.

# Optional: Moduldateien
*.iml

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Editor files
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Temporary files
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
*.swp
*.swo
*~